<h2 class="center">ABSTRACT</h2>
<p>The Smart Home Services Management System is an online platform that connects people at home with verified, professional service workers like electricians, plumbers, painters, and cleaners. Our system includes a fully developed Web Application for Residents and Providers, and a Mobile App that has exactly the same features and is currently in its final steps of completion. Both the Web and Mobile apps are connected to a powerful Web Admin dashboard.</p>
<p>Users can easily request a service online. Residents can choose their required service category, write their job details, and use a GPS map to select their exact location. Once a job is posted, nearby verified Providers can see it and offer a price. When both sides agree, they go through a clear, step-by-step booking process (like waiting for inspection, working, and finally completing the job using an OTP verification). The app also has a real-time live chat system where they can talk and share photos easily.</p>
<p>Admins can watch and manage everything. Admins can add or update service categories, check the ID cards (CNIC) of service providers to make sure they are real, and see the profits and total earnings of the platform.</p>
<p>This system is built using the MERN Stack (MongoDB, Express.js, React, Node.js) for the web views and servers, and React Native for the Mobile App. </p>

